{"id": 809, "genre": 1001, "title": "一句话说明你是假期废柴", "description": "假期废柴是一种新型僵尸病毒，被这种病毒感染的人类一到放假就会死去成为僵尸，他们安息在床上，不能见阳光，除了小便、饥饿和关掉歪怀没有谁能复活他们。——Mona Lishark", "record_count": 3292, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160608143547m0Vhlo4FxY9SHnc8.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-07T11:20:36Z", "options": [{"id": 48128, "content": "我就是", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462182}, {"id": 47876, "content": "此时此刻，我就是被子，被子就是我", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60415}, {"id": 47879, "content": "拖延症愈加猖狂", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225060}, {"id": 47627, "content": "除了手机，什么都提不起兴趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 438332}, {"id": 48139, "content": "为什么要过年呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331866}, {"id": 48907, "content": "胖了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465600}, {"id": 48140, "content": "唯一的体力劳动就是睡觉了，不说了，我要休息会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307705}, {"id": 48141, "content": "动一下就会让我身体里的细胞翻天覆地，为了我自己好，还是不要动力吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254678}, {"id": 47633, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461079}, {"id": 47378, "content": "手机在手，天下我有???", "image": null, "praise_count": 636, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 457481}, {"id": 48403, "content": "特么的看完感觉我好勤快。。。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 47380, "content": "宅出霉了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307966}, {"id": 48660, "content": "hagjjtdd", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293936}, {"id": 47381, "content": "不好意思我现在过的是美国时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 103, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228770}, {"id": 48662, "content": "哪有无线   家就在哪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464205}, {"id": 50198, "content": "我跟在英国的哥哥作息时间一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287921}, {"id": 47383, "content": "其实我连我现在这句话都不想打的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 242, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222457}, {"id": 47385, "content": "男朋友今天早上说分手忧伤了十分钟又睡过去了 刚刚才起床?", "image": null, "praise_count": 219, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 394353}, {"id": 48153, "content": "血液以凝固", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462272}, {"id": 48409, "content": "起床靠尿意", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342827}, {"id": 47386, "content": "饿了 睡着了就不饿了", "image": null, "praise_count": 86, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263868}, {"id": 47387, "content": "睡觉吃睡觉吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226745}, {"id": 47388, "content": "就光顾着抢红包了", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456710}, {"id": 47900, "content": "都快忘记怎么跟人交流了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315214}, {"id": 48412, "content": "明天一定做作业！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462459}, {"id": 47389, "content": "我饿 但我起不来", "image": null, "praise_count": 183, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263868}, {"id": 48158, "content": "  其实我现在都不感觉是在过年，感觉在梦中", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462288}, {"id": 47391, "content": "网管加钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460474}, {"id": 47903, "content": "美好的一天从正午开始", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 427231}, {"id": 48927, "content": "咦，今天是几号？听说再过两个星期就开学了???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465682}, {"id": 49695, "content": "有人请吃大餐，我能起床，除此以外，基本都到中午或者起床吃晚饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464039}, {"id": 47392, "content": "吃  over?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456827}, {"id": 47394, "content": "要不是过年，我是不会起来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460499}, {"id": 48162, "content": "能打字我绝不开口 能意会我决不言传", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 418962}, {"id": 49443, "content": "日夜颠倒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467367}, {"id": 47396, "content": "感觉自己已经在发酵了", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460511}, {"id": 47397, "content": "起床太浪费能量了", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280789}, {"id": 47398, "content": "我是等开饭时不能看电脑才摸出手机看这个的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341150}, {"id": 47399, "content": "宅不住的男人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460535}, {"id": 47400, "content": "天天躺着不想动", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460538}, {"id": 47401, "content": "每天被我妈骂三遍起来吃午饭...感觉进入了冬眠期", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 322054}, {"id": 46890, "content": "我的闹钟设的是：14：00", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 47402, "content": "现在还睡着啊，打算躺到晚上吃年夜饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98651}, {"id": 46891, "content": "至今没有吃过早餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 411, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 47403, "content": "有没有好一点的 饿死了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460555}, {"id": 46892, "content": "躺到低血糖，摸一块巧克力吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 133, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 47404, "content": "在床上度过了假期的一半，剩下的在餐桌上度过", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358441}, {"id": 49452, "content": "后天开学 哦不我的作业在哪里？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467381}, {"id": 55340, "content": "一不小心就睡到下午了，家里没人了都", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490571}, {"id": 48429, "content": "再玩半个小时不急然后一天过去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 463074}]}